                  , about one in the night, on the <rs id="t17871024-9-cd44" type="crimeDate">25th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871024-9-off43 t17871024-9-cd44"></join> last, and stealing therein two pieces of pork, weight about eleven pounds, value 5 s. one pig's foot, value 3 d. an iron shovel, value 2 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17871024-9-person126">
                        John
                         Pool
                     <interp inst="t17871024-9-person126" type="surname" value="Pool"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17871024-9-person126" type="given" value="John"></interp>
